************************************
Max AI explores strange, new formats
************************************

You can now get monthly changelog highlights in ultra-nerdy video format ( =
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3DxHR4cOscml4 ) over on our YouTube page. T=
his month the crew of Starship Changelog explore Max AI's new abilities in =
experiments, surveys, and analytics. HD video. Big crunchy pixels.

Watch, like, and subscribe ( https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3DxHR4cOscml4 =
)=E2=80=8Atwo types of hog! ( https://app.posthog.com/settings/user-feature=
-previews )

******************************************
Messaging Workflows now in feature preview
******************************************

We've widened the scope of our messaging product to include a lot more than=
 just emails, and renamed it as=C2=A0workflows. But you can also still send=
 messages with it! Join the preview to start building event-triggered email=
 campaigns in PostHog.=C2=A0

Join the workflows preview ( https://app.posthog.com/settings/user-feature-=
previews )=E2=80=8Atwo types of hog! ( https://posthog.com/blog/data-pipeli=
ne-pricing )

***************************************
It's now cheaper to send data elsewhere
***************************************

TL;DR:=C2=A0We now charge for data pipelines based on=C2=A0rows exported=C2=
=A0and=C2=A0trigger events. It matches our pricing principles better and me=
ans 98% of you will now pay less. You'll also benefit from much bigger free=
 tiers ( https://posthog.com/blog/data-pipeline-pricing ). So, please use d=
ata pipelines more to help us maintain our revenue? The shareholders would =
appreciate it.=C2=A0

Explore 145 possible integrations ( https://posthog.com/cdp )=E2=80=8Atwo t=
ypes of hog! ( https://posthog.com/cdp )

***************************************
Meta Ads now available as a data source
***************************************

We've added Meta Ads as a new data source ( https://posthog.com/cdp ) in Po=
stHog CDP, enabling you to pull campaign data and performance metrics like =
clicks and impressions into PostHog. This sort of data is especially useful=
 for our new Marketing Analytics beta ( https://app.posthog.com/settings/us=
er-feature-previews ) too!

Join the marketing analytics beta ( https://posthog.com/cdp )=E2=80=8Anot l=
ike tab cola though ( https://app.posthog.com/new )

********************************************
Now available: Unlimited tabs, easier search
********************************************

Multi-taskers, rejoice! You can now open multiple tabs within PostHog, givi=
ng you a much better way to organize your work. You can even set the new ta=
b view, with its plentiful shortcuts and Max AI search bar, as your default=
=2E It's very Web 2.0, tbh.

Open a new tab ( https://app.posthog.com/new )=E2=80=8A
Want more? Head to the full changelog ( https://posthog.com/changelog/2025 =
)

